{"tid":1339622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大學生會721支援","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:29:31.000Z","uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd0880885fbf8339ad53036444939f16a724647","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"【城大學生會法律支援】<br />\n<br />\n警方於上環一帶出示橙旗並已開槍；元朗一帶有白衫人士毆打市民，請各城大同學小心務必注意安全並注意安全。如需被捕支援，請盡快聯絡本會：<br />\n署理外務副會長邵嵐：56477696 (tg/whatsapp/sms)<br />\n學生會辦公室：34425570<br />\n<br />\n若有城大同學不幸被捕或知道有人被捕，請盡快通知本會被捕者以下資料：<br />\n1. 中英文全名<br />\n2. 性別<br />\n3. 就讀科目及年級<br />\n4. 身份證號碼<br />\n5. 電話號碼<br />\n6. 正前往之警署(如適用)<br />\n7. 緊急聯絡人電話號碼<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【城大學生會現開放休息中心】<br />\n<br />\n學生會現開放位中國銀行香港綜合樓7樓之R7200室作休息中心，同學若有需要可前往稍作休息或簡單處理傷口。<br />\n<br />\n如有任何查詢請聯絡：<br />\n署理外務副會長邵嵐：56477696<br />\n學生會辦公室：34425570"},{"pid":"b1a377a45f52e4f54b8dacf4dc6f28f8bae8ccf2","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69c3fdda810ea29f5c0cf69b75ade1e1c1e277c7","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cd0fbf3d6bdc69cd30a435f2c7a15f6775481c5","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ca193a2361528e52df452e7cc8724369d7505d8","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e718ffe72df4fcfa1b7e90b0e4aebafdc6836a34","tid":1339622,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"推"}]}